{"word":"G4932 - συντέμνω - syntémnō - soon-tem'-no - Short","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συντέμνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">syntémnō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soon-tem'-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Short</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சீக்கிரம் நிறைவேற்று"},{"paragraph":"1. to cut to pieces"},{"paragraph":"2. to cut short"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G5114 - τομώτερος - tomṓteros - tom-o'-ter-os/5114\">G5114</a>; to <i>contract</i> by cutting, that is, (figuratively) <i>do concisely</i> (<i>speedily</i>): - (cut) short.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}